The paper focuses on detecting and combating fake news through online fact-checking systems and user engagement. This falls under the categories of social media analysis (cs.SI), natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SOC), and cybersecurity (cs.CYBER).
